content.title: Timex Men's Easy Reader Watch
content.top_review:
This was a gift for my father. He wanted an easy to read analog watch with day and date. Timex hit this one out of the park. It checked all boxes and has a great leather band. My Dad said it was easy to set up and "it is just the right size, not like those huge watches these days." So this was a win!
  
Read more
